name: ASWebAuthenticationSessionRequestDelegate
desc: An interface through which the session request can inform its delegate, which is typically a browser, about the outcome of the authentication attempt.

items.name: func authenticationSessionRequest(ASWebAuthenticationSessionRequest, didCompleteWithCallbackURL: URL)
items.desc: Tells the delegate, typically a browser, that the authentication completed successfully.

items.name: func authenticationSessionRequest(ASWebAuthenticationSessionRequest, didCancelWithError: Error)
items.desc: Tells the delegate, typically a browser, that the authentication was canceled.
